title: Episode 115: Leverage Podcast Interview w/ Jared Psych Lawrence - Building A Social Circle
description:
In this episode, Robbie and Jared discuss a multitude of topics from approaching women in social circles, Jared’s new book, and even intermittent fasting.

Show Notes:

Modern Flirting’s #1 method for creating attraction? 1:00

The “I know it when I see it principle” 4:12

A tip to rapidly speed up your learning process and get faster results on your journey to improve your love life 8:05

A one-time special offer from Jared… 13:50

How long it took Jared to write his book and the strategies he used for finishing in time… 14:45

What to do if you run out of shit to say… 17:46

The tragic mistake guys make in group situations… 22:12

The secret to the social life, work life balance dilemma… 31:38

How to decide if your city is worth building a social circle in… 34:25

What to do if your work life starts suffering… 40:32

The social circle impacts on your health and fitness… 43:20

A new app that will allow you to stay in shape with very little work… 44:43

The surprising benefits of intermittent fasting and how it can get you ripped 46:42

The “Fuckboys” vs. the “Players” 51:50

Who are naturals and what is their role in a social circle? 56:45

The #1 key to making sure you don’t cockblock yourself on the 5 yard-line. Don’t make this  tragic, rookie mistake! 60:18

The answer to the question… when should I text her? 62:08

How to break your bad pickup habits in social settings 63:56

The secret for finding the sweet spot between too little and too much energy… 66:51

I'm Robbie Kramer 🎙Host of The Inner Confidence Podcast & Founder of Inner Confidence, Inc.

I lived an exhilarating single life filled with adventures and lessons, and ultimately achieved what I had always aspired to – finding an amazing, feminine, and loving wife. 

I believe my experiences provide a rare balance of wild freedom and committed love, equipping me with the insights to help you navigate the complexities of dating and relationships in today's world. Let me guide you to embrace your desires, improve your social prowess, and ultimately attract the partner who aligns with your highest aspirations.

You won’t find any fluffy, new-age, or cringy stuff here, just tested, proven and actionable advice that yields results.

Apply to join our exclusive Inner Confidence Community of ambitious men who are actively working together to achieve their goals faster   ► https://innerconfidence.com/community

You can email me at robbie@innerconfidence.com with any questions or comments.
